      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You\u2019ve gotta see this absolute beauty! I have taken such good care of this car, and it truly shows\u2014it looks and feels just like it did the day it left the lot. It's been my pride and joy, pampered and kept in top-notch shape. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for a new home where it'll be just as loved. If you're looking for a ride that's been treated with total TLC, you've found it! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
