    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours-level condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine, characterized by its high-revving 8,000 RPM redline and six individual throttle bodies. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. This vehicle has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement. The chassis dynamics are factory-sharp, with no bushing deflection or hydraulic leaks. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the aesthetic condition is flawless, exhibiting original paint depth and pristine interior bolsters. A true analog masterpiece for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 46500.0,
