    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2019 Porsche 718 Cayman is a true 'time capsule' vehicle for the most discerning enthusiast. Finished in a vibrant Guards Red with a deep, mirror-like gloss, the exterior is entirely free of rock chips, swirls, or any blemishes. It has been exclusively garage-kept under a soft cover and has never been driven in inclement weather. The interior is equally pristine, featuring Black leather that remains supple with firm bolsters and a factory-fresh matte finish on the steering wheel. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at an authorized Porsche dealership, and I have a comprehensive binder of all maintenance records and original documentation. The alloy wheels are flawless, wrapped in a fresh set of Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires, and the undercarriage is as clean as the day it left the factory. This car represents a rare opportunity to acquire a modern sports car in its purest, most untouched form.",
      "price": 48500.0,
